FBIS3-23158 "jptot010__l94121" JPRS-TOT-94-010-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 10 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA LEBANON Bomb in Zuq Musbih Church Kills 10, Injures 40 Fadlallah Denounces Bombing, Blames Israel NC2702191394 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 27 Feb 94 NC2702191394 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] 'Allamah Muhammad Husayn Fadlallah called the bombing at Sayyidat al-Najat Church an atrocity and lamented the death of innocents. The bombing, he said, signals a new pattern of attacks on places of worship. He added that the crime is designed to disturb the country's security and political life and unsettle the public's renewed sense of civic peace. Israeli hands cannot be absolved of this crime, whose purpose was to divert attention from the massacre at the Ibrahimi Mosque and trigger a new cycle of violence in the country, Fadlallah stated. He called on the authorities to uncover the evil hands that carried out the crime.
